21:48.920 --> 21:49.310
Ya.

21:49.830 --> 21:50.240
Benar.

21:50.440 --> 21:51.040
Saya tahu.

21:51.480 --> 21:51.880
Benar.

21:51.960 --> 21:53.240
Kelak, dalam bidang porselin biru putih...

21:53.240 --> 21:53.900
Oh ya, ayah.

21:54.590 --> 21:55.350
Saya ada urusan lain,

21:55.350 --> 21:56.590
