22:36.920 --> 22:38.240
Tak berat.

22:39.440 --> 22:40.970
Mak sangat risau akan awak.

22:41.790 --> 22:42.990
Saya pergi dulu, mak.

22:43.310 --> 22:44.070
Cen,

22:44.270 --> 22:45.550
