25:53.640 --> 25:54.510
Cepat, saya ajar awak.

25:54.510 --> 25:55.350
Tak nak.

25:55.350 --> 25:56.350
Hulurkan tangan.

25:56.480 --> 25:57.720
Sangat seronok.

25:57.720 --> 25:57.830
Ambil balik, saya tak nak.

25:57.830 --> 25:59.400
Ambil balik, saya tak nak.

26:00.160 --> 26:00.640
Yi,

26:00.960 --> 26:03.760
