26:26.160 --> 26:27.880
Sekian sahaja siaran langsung hari ini.

26:27.880 --> 26:28.680
Terima kasih.

26:33.720 --> 26:34.310
Xiaqing.

26:34.750 --> 26:36.350
Cantiknya hasil kerja awak.

26:36.790 --> 26:38.160
Terima kasih kerana menyukainya.

26:38.160 --> 26:39.890
Jenama kami bernama Gorgeous.

26:40.000 --> 26:41.260
Ikutilah jenama kami.

26:42.110 --> 26:43.400
